{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<msubsup>","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>MathML <code>&lt;msubsup&gt;</code> 元素用于为表达式同时附加上角标和下角标。</p>\n\n<p>它的语法如下：<code>&lt;msubsup&gt; <em>base subscript superscript</em> &lt;/msubsup&gt;</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"class\"><code>class</code>、<code>id</code>、<code>style</code></dt>\n <dd>供<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS\">样式</a>使用。</dd>\n <dt id=\"href\"><code>href</code></dt>\n <dd>Used to set a hyperlink to a specified URI.</dd>\n <dt id=\"mathbackground\"><code>mathbackground</code></dt>\n <dd>背景颜色。支持 <code>#rgb</code>、<code>#rrggbb</code> 和 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">HTML 颜色名称 (en-US)</a>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"mathcolor\"><code>mathcolor</code></dt>\n <dd>文本颜色。支持 <code>#rgb</code>、<code>#rrggbb</code> 和 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">HTML 颜色名称 (en-US)</a>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"subscriptshift\"><code>subscriptshift</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>The minimum space by which to shift the subscript below the baseline of the expression, as a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values#lengths\">length value.</a><br>\n This attribute is deprecated and will be removed in the future.</dd>\n <dt id=\"superscriptshift\"><code>superscriptshift</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>The minimum space by which to shift the superscript above the baseline of the expression, as a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values#lengths\">length value.</a><br>\n This attribute is deprecated and will be removed in the future.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>示例渲染结果：<img alt=\"x1\" src=\"/files/3204/msubsup.png\" style=\"margin-left: 10px; vertical-align: middle;\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>当前浏览器中的渲染结果：<math displaystyle=\"true\"> <msubsup><mo>∫</mo> <mn> 0 </mn> <mn> 1 </mn> </msubsup> </math></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">displaystyle</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>true<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>msubsup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token entity\" title=\"∫\">&amp;#x222B;</span><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 积分符号 --&gt;</span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> 0 <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> 1 <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>msubsup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">备注</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter3.html#presm.msubsup\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 3.0<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">msubsup</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Current specification</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML2/chapter3.html#presm.msubsup\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 2.0<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">msubsup</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial specification</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"mathml.elements.msubsup","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\" title=\"<msub>\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></code>（上标）</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\" title=\"<msup>\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></code>（下标）</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt; (en-US)</a></code>（Prescript 和 tensor indice）</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"MathML <msubsup> 元素用于为表达式同时附加上角标和下角标。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<msubsup>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<msubsup>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<msubsup>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/mathml/element/msubsup","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/mathml/element/msubsup/index.html","las